videos.headline: No. 14 Razorbacks best Braves in season opener
videos.description: Khalif Battle drops a game-high 21 points as two of his teammates also tack on double-digit performances and Arkansas cruises past Alcorn State, 93-59.

videos.description: Arkansas forward Trevon Brazile flies to the rack for a massive dunk over a defender.
